### Next Steps for Deployment
To enable Web Analytics tracking on Vercel:
1. Deploy the project to Vercel
2. Navigate to your project dashboard on Vercel
3. Go to Analytics tab
4. Click the "Enable" button to activate Web Analytics

The code implementation is complete and ready for deployment. Once enabled in the Vercel dashboard, the Analytics component will automatically track page views and Web Vitals metrics.

